{"tid":498043,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人執到粒咪咪","createTime":"2017-12-13T11:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T12:42:51.000Z","uid":162981,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"22ff47ea8a9abad34756cc2b1f130ca8edc81103","tid":498043,"uid":162981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"有個FD踢波個陣甩左粒LIN<br />\n<br />\n話說佢唔著衫踢<br />\n<br />\n之後就入左波<br />\n<br />\n跟住學D足球員胸貼地咁滑地下<br />\n<br />\n點知一滑個下<br />\n<br />\n捽甩左粒lin<br />\n<br />\n我哋成班FD見到已經笑到仆街<br />\n<br />\n咁我哋就叫白車啦<br />\n<br />\n聽電話個個都笑住問我哋喺邊到咁<br />\n<br />\n之後去到醫院<br />\n<br />\n個醫生問粒LIN去咗邊<br />\n<br />\n我個FD話:粒LIN有用㗎?唔撚係呀??<br />\n<br />\n粒LIN而家應該仲係球場到<br />\n<br />\n咁返去搵已經唔見左<br />\n<br />\n我個FD就係咁冇咗粒LIN"},{"pid":"5c1a2ff4e8bacbeaaf7446a7f40eda8f0df49925","tid":498043,"uid":28113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 心地唔好呀"},{"pid":"c1a2b39bc367b7ed4fa7521d95f8eb0ed778d58f","tid":498043,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b923f23d9f87a683c62a92a77184adf034c56fe9","tid":498043,"uid":14275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我頭行過以為係軟糖<br />\n食左</blockquote><br />\n嗰兩粒軟嘅綿花糖 亦都變左兩粒硬嘅橡皮糖啦"}]}